product_name: Superfeet Green Premium Insoles - High Volume
long_description: These green Superfeet(R) insoles align and control the motion of your feet, providing balance, support and shock absorption for hiking and other active sports. High-volume insoles take up extra volume in footwear, making them ideal for loose-fitting shoes or narrow feet. Full-length closed-cell foam provides cushioning, while 3/4-length polypropylene heel caps stabilize feet inside boots. Deep heel pockets, rockered bottoms and strategically placed cut-outs allow for natural shock absorption. Superfeet recommends this green style for use in footwear with removable insoles; also recommended for Gore-Tex(R) footwear.
